## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="45654-102">启用智能标签后，图表将重新定位重叠的数据点标签基于一组用户定义的规则。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-102">When smart labels are enabled, the chart repositions overlapping data point labels, based on a set of user-defined rules.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="45654-103">将绘制标注线条链接其数据点标签。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-103">Callout lines will be drawn to link the label with its data point.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="45654-104">可以控制标注线条的可视特性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-104">The visual attributes of the callout line can be controlled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="45654-105">这些可视特性包括颜色、 线条样式和线条宽度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-105">These visual attributes include color, line style, and line width.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="45654-106"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>和<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A>属性控制的修饰符，如箭头，显示的标注线条末尾。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-106">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> properties control the embellishments, such as arrowheads, that appear at the end of the callout line.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="45654-107"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A>属性可以设置为任何<xref:System.Drawing.Color>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-107">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A> property can be set to any <xref:System.Drawing.Color> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="45654-108">如果你设置标注线条的颜色，还会自动将设置的颜色<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A>和所定义的修饰符<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-108">If you set the color of the callout line, you will also automatically set the color of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the embellishment defined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="45654-109"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A>属性控制的标注线条的像素宽度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-109">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A> property controls the pixel width of the callout line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="45654-110">使用此属性也将缩放的修饰符<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A>和<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-110">Use of this property will also scale the embellishments of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="45654-111">可以通过使用多个运动相关属性控制智能标签的移动。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-111">The movement of smart labels can be controlled through the use of several motion-related properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="45654-112">这些将定义移动的方向，距离的规则和指示的数据点标签是否允许将保留在绘图区。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-112">These define the rules of movement for the direction, distance and whether the data point label is allowed to leave the plotting area.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="45654-113">默认移动规则通常将解决大多数问题。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-113">The default movement rules will normally resolve most issues.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="45654-114"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A>定义一个值，指定以像素为单位的数据的最大距离情况下允许使用数据点标签移开重叠的点。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-114">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> defines a value that specifies the maximum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels are allowed to be moved in case of overlapping.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="45654-115"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A>属性定义一个值，指定以像素为单位的数据的最小距离点，将发生重叠移动数据点标签。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-115">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> property defines a value that specifies the minimum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels will be moved in case of overlapping.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="45654-116">当数据点标签需要可重新定位时，标签将至少移动指定的像素数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-116">When a data point label needs to be repositioned, the label will be moved by at least the number of pixels specified.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="45654-117"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A>属性指示是否当重叠问题无法解析时是否隐藏标签。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-117">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property indicates whether the labels are hidden when overlapping issues cannot be resolved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="45654-118">如果<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A>属性是`true`，无法在指定的区域内绘制数据点和<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A>和<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A>中所允许的方向<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>，将不绘制数据点标签。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-118">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property is `true`, and the data point cannot be drawn within the area specified by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> in the directions allowed by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>, the data point label will not be drawn.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="45654-119"><xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>属性定义可以在其中移动数据点标签的方向。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-119">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A> property defines the direction(s) in which the data point label can be moved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="45654-120">此属性接受一个<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>值或按位 OR，多个<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-120">This property accepts one <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> value or a bitwise-OR of multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="45654-121">默认值是位或所有<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles>值，以允许在所有可能的方向不同点的数据中心重新定位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-121">The default is the bitwise-OR of all <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values, to allow repositioning in all possible directions except to the center of the data point.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="45654-122">以下图表类型不支持智能标签：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-122">Smart labels are not supported for the following chart types:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="45654-123">条形图： 栏和百分比堆积条形图。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-123">Bar charts: bar and hundred-percent-stacked bar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="45654-124">形状图： 饼图、 圆环图、 极坐标图和雷达图图表。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-124">Shape charts: pie, doughnut, polar and radar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="45654-125">范围图： 范围、 范围柱形图和范围条形图。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-125">Range charts: range, range column and range bar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="45654-126">堆积面积图： 堆积面积图和百分比堆积面积图。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="45654-126">Stacked area charts: stacked area and hundred-percent-stacked area charts.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```vb  
Imports System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
Private Function SetSmartLabelsOptions()  
  
   ' Enabling the SmartLabels™ attribute.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.Enabled = true  
  
   ' Set the callout style.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutStyle = LabelCalloutStyle.Underlined  
  
   ' Set the callout line color.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineColor = Color.Goldenrod;  
  
   ' Set the callout line style.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineStyle = ChartDashStyle.Dash  
  
   ' Set the callout line width.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineWidth = 3   
  
   ' Set the callout line anchor cap.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineAnchorCap = LineAnchorCap.Arrow  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
using System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
private void SetSmartLabelsOptions()  
{  
   // Enabling the SmartLabels™ attribute.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.Enabled = true;  
  
   // Set the callout style.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutStyle = LabelCalloutStyle.Underlined;  
  
   // Set the callout line color.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineColor = Color.Goldenrod;  
  
   // Set the callout line style.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineStyle = ChartDashStyle.Dash;  
  
   // Set the callout line width.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineWidth = 3;  
  
   // Set the callout line anchor cap.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineAnchorCap = LineAnchorCap.Arrow;  
}  
```
